Woody De Othello (amụrụ n'afọ 1991) bụ ónyé America na-ese ite na ónyé na-ese ihe. Ọ bi ma na-arụ ọrụ na San Francisco Bay Area, California.
A mụrụ Wood De Othello na 1991 nà Miami, Florida. Ọ bụ onye Haiti.
Othello nwetara ákàrá ugo mmụta BFA na Mahadum Florida Atlantic na Boca Raton, na ákàrá ugo mmụta MFA na California College of Arts na San Francisco na 2017.

N'afọ 2015, emere ihe ngosi nké mbụ nkè Othello, It's Going To Be Ok, na gallery Unit ótụ na Lake Worth, Florida. N'afọ 2018, a gụnyere Othello na Yerba Buena Center for the Arts triennial exhibition, "Bay Area Now 8." N'afọ 2019, San Jose Museum of Art kwadoro, Woody De Othello: Ụlọ iku ume. Looking In, ihe ngosi nkè ọrụ Othello na Jessica Silverman Gallery na 2021 gụnyere ihe ọkpụkpụ, ihe osise, na ọrụ ndị e dere na akwụkwọ.
N'afọ 2022 a họpụtara Othello kà ọ sonye na 2022 Whitney Biennial, nkè Adrienne Edwards na David Breslin haziri.

Ọrụ Othello dị na nchịkọta nke ọtụtụ ebe ngosi nka nke oge a gụnyere: Institute of Contemporary Art, Miami; San Francisco Museum of Modern Art; San Jose Museum of Art, San Jose, California; na Renwick Gallery, Smithsonian American Art Museum, Washington D.C.
